Title: To Mogujia
Description:
Throm-ka, $c. While we were busy defending our foothold here, Regent Lord Lor'themar Theron led a research expedition north into Kun-Lai Summit.

Unfortunately, it seems they have encountered trouble.

Warchief Garrosh Hellscream has already departed to lend his assistance, but he will require additional reinforcements.

Go northward into the mountains of Kun-Lai. Speak to Tak-Tak for transportation.
ObjectivesText: Find Regent Lord Lor'themar Theron at Mogujia. Speak to Tak-Tak at Domination Point for transportation.
